        <updateDate>2025-03-12T10:39:24Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Homeowners Premium Tax Reduction Act of 2025&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill establishes a new deduction of up to $10,000 claimed against gross income (above-the-line tax deduction) for annual policy premiums paid or incurred for homeowners insurance on an individual's principal residence.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
